```

---

### **9. /delete**
**Kya karta hai:** File delete karta hai  
**Kab use kare:** File remove karni ho  
**Syntax:**
```
/delete filename.ext
```
**Warning:** Permanent delete, recover nahi hoga

---

### **10. /list**
**Kya karta hai:** Current directory ki files dikhata hai  
**Kab use kare:** Project structure dekhna ho  
**Syntax:**
```
/list
```
**Alternative:** `/ls`

---

### **11. /tree**
**Kya karta hai:** Full folder structure tree format mein  
**Kab use kare:** Complete project structure dekhna ho  
**Syntax:**
```
/tree
```

---

### **12. /save**
**Kya karta hai:** Changes save karta hai  
**Kab use kare:** Kaam save karna ho  
**Syntax:**
```
/save
```
**Alternative:** Auto-save ON hai usually

---

### **13. /rename**
**Kya karta hai:** File ka naam change karta hai  
**Kab use kare:** File rename karni ho  
**Syntax:**
```
/rename oldname.ext newname.ext
```
**Example:**
```
/rename app.js main.js
```

---

### **14. /move**
**Kya karta hai:** File ko doosri location mein move karta hai  
**Kab use kare:** File ka location change karna ho  
**Syntax:**
```
/move filename.ext new/path/
```

---

### **15. /copy**
**Kya karta hai:** File ka duplicate banata hai  
**Kab use kare:** Backup banana ho  
**Syntax:**
```
/copy source.ext destination.ext
```

